* Mapear tecla CAPS a Control
/usr/share/X11/xkb/symbols/es
xkb_symbols "basic" {
..
    replace key <CAPS>  {  [ Control_L, Control_L ] };
    modifier_map  Control { <CAPS>, <LCTL> };
..
}

